WEBVTT

00:02.159 --> 00:04.794
Why did you get a genetic test?

00:05.028 --> 00:06.828
You're so young.

00:06.863 --> 00:08.898
I...

00:08.932 --> 00:12.967
My brother has a genetic disorder.

00:13.002 --> 00:14.802
So when the doctor offered the test,

00:14.836 --> 00:16.837
I just thought, "yeah, I should do that."

00:16.872 --> 00:18.806
I never actually expected...

00:21.877 --> 00:24.245
Oh my god. Oh my god.

00:27.015 --> 00:28.916
You have to tell Toby.

00:28.950 --> 00:31.785
If I tell him, then it's really happening.

00:31.819 --> 00:34.254
It's already happening.

00:34.289 --> 00:36.990
And you shouldn't be dealing
with this on your own.

00:37.025 --> 00:39.492
But he won't even talk to me.

00:41.195 --> 00:43.230
Just tell him the truth and he will.

00:45.565 --> 00:47.400
Do you want me to go with you?

00:50.070 --> 00:51.370
(Knocking)

00:57.477 --> 00:59.145
We need to talk.

01:01.013 --> 01:02.680
I don't have anything to say.

01:05.349 --> 01:08.653
You made it pretty clear you
think you're too good for me.

01:08.687 --> 01:09.988
I'm pregnant.

01:13.212 --> 01:14.745
Are you sure?

01:14.780 --> 01:16.081
Of course I'm sure!

01:16.115 --> 01:19.049
- Do you think I'm making this up?
- Well, is it mine?

01:19.084 --> 01:21.685
Yes. It's yours.

01:23.088 --> 01:25.021
How is that such a terrible thing to ask?

01:25.056 --> 01:28.024
- You said you were into somebody else.
- I said I was confused.

01:28.059 --> 01:30.427
I also said that nothing happened with him.

01:30.462 --> 01:32.796
I was faithful to you.

01:32.830 --> 01:35.431
I was honest with you all along.

01:35.466 --> 01:38.000
- I didn't do anything wrong.
- Wait.

01:38.034 --> 01:40.570
Do you know how hard that
was for me to tell you?

01:40.604 --> 01:43.106
Do you know what it's
been like living with this

01:43.140 --> 01:44.607
by myself for weeks?

01:44.641 --> 01:47.410
I've been panicked every minute of the day.

01:48.812 --> 01:51.180
You are equally responsible for this

01:51.215 --> 01:52.847
and I thought you should know.

01:55.451 --> 01:57.952
Thank you for making this so easy.

