37:23.495 --> 37:25.895
- _
- we use the verb <i>ser</i>

37:25.899 --> 37:28.543
- _
- followed by the feminine article before the hour.

37:28.578 --> 37:29.850
For example,

37:29.851 --> 37:32.233
- _
-  to say it's 2:00 would be <i>son</i>

37:32.234 --> 37:34.485
- _
- las dos.

37:34.549 --> 37:37.017
