37:37.051 --> 37:39.353
- _
- <i>Son las dos y cinco.</i>

37:39.387 --> 37:41.655
- _
- It's two minutes past 5:00.

37:41.690 --> 37:44.758
Minutes can also be
subtracted from the hour.

37:44.793 --> 37:47.126
So for example, how would we say

37:47.160 --> 37:51.631
